data.title: Collin County
data.meta_description: Collin County | 5,916 followers on LinkedIn. Welcome to Collin County, one of the fastest growing counties in Texas and the nation. More than 1,000,000 people and growing. Collin County is located in North Texas, just north of Dallas, with the county seat located in  the city of McKinney.
